[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s6/the_bc_card.mp3" volume="0.0" bus="Voice"]
The B.C. card sits on the pedestal beside the sculpture.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s6/the_wind_ruffles.mp3" volume="0.0" bus="Voice"]
The wind ruffles its edge, but it stays in place.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s6/three_lessons_learned.mp3" volume="0.0" bus="Voice"]
Three lessons learned. Three mysteries solved.
[voice path="res://assets/audio/voice/Chapter 3/c3s6/but_the_chain.mp3" volume="0.0" bus="Voice"]
